node.text:
Craving a delish summer BBQ side dish without all the hassle? Me too! #WWPartner 

Luckily, I’ve cracked the code on pasta salad with my new #Rossipe that’s easy, super @WW friendly, and outrageously yummy! What’s my secret ingredient? Watch to find out & go to ww.com/Ross for more #Rossipes or search “Ross Mathews” in the WW app!

node.title: ROSSIPE: Chic Chickpea Chicken Summer Salad!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Ross Mathews in The Roost Lounge with @drwgarcia. May be an image of 4 people and indoor.

node.text: Karaoke tonight with friends. 🥰 We didn’t sing (I usually do), but it was so fun to sit in our little corner & hear people belt. Scott & I have been friends for nearly 20 years. I used to deliver his mail as an intern on The Tonight Show. Then, when I was happily thrust onto TV, he was there, guiding me every step of the way. We’ve been lifelong friends ever since. We should all be so lucky! ❤️

node.text: THANK YOU @televisionacad for nominating us again this year!!! Creating, hosting and producing TV has been my dream since I was just a little kid and I am grateful for every single second of this extraordinary journey. 🥰 Congrats to the entire hard working team at @RuPaulsDragRace, @worldofwonder, @vh1 & all the queens for an amazing season 13, filmed last summer under unparalleled & historic Covid restrictions. It’s an honor to work with you. ❤️ And congrats to all the other nominees! 🏆
